  "detailed_description": "Breen Origins aims to bring a fun experience to the FPS genre. It is a back to basics, boots on the ground game, where the only thing that matters is your skill and how you choose to use it. This is a multiplayer experience where players can play game modes like Gun Race, Team deathmatch, Capture the flag or Free-For-All Modes. <br><br>Breen Origins is built with Unity and will expand throughout the Early Access period.<br><br><strong>\"Never turn your back on a Breen.\"</strong><br><i>—Romulan maxim (DS9 episode: \"By Inferno's Light\")</i>",
